    "topic": "multivariable_calculus",
    "problem": "Evaluate \\(\\displaystyle\\int_0^{1}\\int_0^{1}(x+y)\\,dx\\,dy\\).",
    "choices": {"A": "\\(\\tfrac12\\)", "B": "\\(1\\)", "C": "\\(2\\)", "D": "\\(\\tfrac14\\)", "E": "\\(\\tfrac32\\)"},
    "answer": "B",
    "solution": "Inner integral: \\(\\int_0^1(x+y)\\,dx=\\tfrac12+y\\). Then \\(\\int_0^1\\left(\\tfrac12+y\\right)dy=\\tfrac12+\\tfrac12=\\boxed{1}\\)."
  },
